data.description: Step into luxury living in this charming two-story home nestled within a gated community. The open floorplan is ideal for seamless living and entertaining, with a kitchen showcasing granite countertops, a breakfast bar island, and stainless steel appliances. Downstairs flooring is tile throughout with the warm look of wood.  Upstairs, the bedrooms offer privacy, with the primary bedroom boasting an ensuite full bath with a double vanity. Laundry room conveniently located on 2nd floor close to bedrooms. Enjoy tranquil outdoor living on the deck overlooking a serene wooded park area, complete with a retractable sun shade on one side. Unwind in the hot tub as you soak in the sounds of nature surrounding you.
